# Web Dev Agent — deployment config
# Copy to .env and fill in your values (never commit .env).
#
# Web Dev implements code changes in a cloned repository. All SCM operations
# (clone, branch, push, PR) are dispatched to the SCM Agent via A2A protocol.
# Git credentials belong in the SCM Agent .env, not here.
#
# Non-credential config (runtime, model, registry) inherits from
# config/constellation.yaml.

# ----- OPTIONAL: service binding -----
# HOST=0.0.0.0
# PORT=8050
